      <content>&lt;p&gt;for a little side project, i needed small usb cams, preferably for free.
i still had old hp elitebooks 8440p, and from their display, i removed the camera, see the picture below.
the picture shows always the pinout.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;next, i soldered the 4 cables together, leaving the GPIO pin unused. no big deal, there is no faster way to get an usb-cam for raspberry and co.&lt;/p&gt;
